snippet.title: A Bump in the Road | Millie Inbetween - Series 2, Episode 11 | ZeeKay
snippet.description:
Tired, cramped and working too hard, Dad and Amber realise they need some space – so decide to take a break from their relationship. The kids are gutted, but determined that their own friendships will survive. Their efforts to keep them apart, though, mean Dad and Amber become friends again…but only friends. To get them beyond the dreaded Friendzone is the kids’ biggest challenge yet.
